"  Ham:","1  (8-pound) 33%-less-sodium smoked, fully cooked ham half","2 tablespoons apricot preserves","2 tablespoons Dijon mustard","1/2 cup brown sugar","1/2 cup gingersnap crumbs (about 9 cookies, finely crushed)","  Sauce:","1 1/2 cups apricot preserves","1/2 cup dry Marsala wine","3 tablespoons Dijon mustard","1/2 teaspoon ground allspice"